com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.linearpathmatch
Class LinearPath

java.lang.Object
  com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.linearpathmatch.LinearPath
public class LinearPath
extends java.lang.Object

A contiguous set of LinearEdges. Although not strictly enforced, most uses of this class are expected to represent paths that self-intersect at most at their endpoints.

Version:
1.0
